data.description: In the heart of RAYBURN COUNTRY, sits this beautiful golf course home on the 7th Fairway. As you walk thru the front door and into the foyer, you will be amazed at the size of the grand living room straight ahead. To the left sits the formal dining that can be used for a formal sitting area, office, or kids playroom! The kitchen and breakfast area is off the back of the living room. The sun room is great for entertaining and is just steps away from the wet bar. The master en-suite opens up to the courtyard in the back. With spacious bedrooms throughout, this home is great. Several built-ins throughout the house as well as a stereo system that can be heard in every room! Outside you will find the double attached garage and also a golf cart bay that makes accessing the golf course with ease. AC unit and roof is only 4 years old! With almost 3300 square feet, this property has endless possibilities! From full time living to income producing, this is a must see!
